      "instruction": "<p>Boil a full kettle</p><p>While the chicken is cooking, dissolve your<strong> chicken stock mix </strong>in 150ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[225ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> in half</p>",
