      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely slice (don't chop!) your<strong> garlic</strong></p><p>Trim, then add your<strong> green beans</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for an initial 2-3 min</p>",
